<h1 id='contribution'>Contribution</h1>
<p>The communication protocols are based on the work of researchers and engineers in many countries. They are an open living standard by the community, for the community.</p>

<p>We invite you to join and contribute to them on <a href="https://github.com/DAVFoundation" target="blank">GitHub</a>.</p>
